   "x": 96,
   "y": 1658,
   "width": 660,
   "height": 104,
   "text": "ScheduledRequests.scheduled_mm_encoder_items\n  \u2192 existing SerializableSchedulerOutput only when schedule propagation is needed\nPP: first stage schedules; every PP rank reconstructs and currently runs the MM encoder\nExecutor: retry gate \u2192 MM forward \u2192 resource preparation \u2192 LLM forward\nEncoder-only progress still runs when the LLM batch is empty",
   "originalText": "ScheduledRequests.scheduled_mm_encoder_items\n  \u2192 existing SerializableSchedulerOutput only when schedule propagation is needed\nPP: first stage schedules; every PP rank reconstructs and currently runs the MM encoder\nExecutor: retry gate \u2192 MM forward \u2192 resource preparation \u2192 LLM forward\nEncoder-only progress still runs when the LLM batch is empty",
